business, all right?

291
00:25:53,385 --> 00:25:56,095
Let's just see about this
ghost, all right?

292
00:25:56,430 --> 00:25:59,766
Come here. Come on.
Over here. Check here.

293
00:26:01,560 --> 00:26:03,394
