a new student today.

479
00:42:38,640 --> 00:42:41,767
I'd like you all to
meet Harvey Kathleen.

480
00:42:44,479 --> 00:42:48,148
Would you like to come up
and say hi to everyone for me?

481
00:43:04,499 --> 00:43:08,502
