492
00:43:45,206 --> 00:43:49,042
I know it looks kind of funky and stuf
from the outside and everything

493
00:43:49,168 --> 00:43:53,213
but, I mean... I don't know,
inside it's kind of cool.

494
00:43:54,007 --> 00:43:56,049
