799
01:12:44,485 --> 01:12:48,488
This Dr. Harvey's got
a lot of spirit, you know
what I'm saying?

800
01:12:48,614 --> 01:12:52,117
Yeah, but he's got his
whole miserable life
ahead of him.

801
01:12:52,243 --> 01:12:55,829
